### Test Languages API Endpoints

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5081

### 1. Get all languages
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Languages

### 2. Get all languages with usage statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Languages/with-usage

### 3. Get language by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Languages/1

### 4. Get language by name
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Languages/name/Python

### 5. Get language by name (case insensitive)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Languages/name/java

### 6. Get language usage statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Languages/1/usage

### 7. Create a new language
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Languages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "languageName": "Go"
}

### 8. Create another language
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Languages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "languageName": "Rust"
}

